    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but it still feels like there's something working against me. it's like even when i pay extra, the math seems designed to keep me stuck in this loop. can you show me a quick example or a formula of how the interest is actually calculated each month vs the principal? i want to see the actual breakdown.",
